Package: epmr
Title: Tools for Educational and Psychological Measurement
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Anthony", "Albano", email = "tony.d.albano@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Contains tools for creating and evaluating educational and
    psychological measures, as used in the book Introduction to Educational and
    Psychological Measurement. Methods support statistical analysis of item
    performance, reliability, validity, and dimensionality, within both classical
    and item response theory frameworks.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.3)
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
